WEBVTT

00:00:08.775 --> 00:00:10.095
My thanks to you both

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:12.075
I will take it from here

00:00:18.149 --> 00:00:19.399
Sure you don't need a hand?

00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:21.725
Quite sure

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:24.075
Wow... 

00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:28.350
So what's your secret, hmm? Let me guess...

00:00:30.075 --> 00:00:31.075
Who knows

00:00:32.125 --> 00:00:34.950
Maybe it's just your sense of responsibility

00:00:36.950 --> 00:00:37.750
Sounds about right

00:01:08.850 --> 00:01:11.700
A day may come when the prophecy is fulfilled

00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:13.900
And the waters burst forth... 

00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:16.450
But it is not this day

00:01:19.275 --> 00:01:23.175
This ancient power could easily obliterate an entire race...

00:01:25.425 --> 00:01:26.975
The tsunami of fury

00:01:27.700 --> 00:01:30.150
Would unleash endless catastrophe

00:01:44.475 --> 00:01:46.725
This sentence is too severe

00:01:47.650 --> 00:01:49.725
Forgive me for overruling it

